Once the emotional connection is made, the scammer will ask for money, often claiming an emergency situation, such as hospital bills or an injured pet. The victim often feels like they are contributing to a good cause, and will continue to send money in order to keep helping the person they feel they have fallen in love with. It is important to be aware of this form of scam as it can cause victims to lose a significant amount of money.
